$PROBLEM    2 compartment fitting
$INPUT       ID TIME AMT DV WTKG GENDER AGE RATE
$DATA      ..\..\datalarge.csv IGNORE=@
           
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4 
$PK      
  CWTKGONE = WTKG/70  ;; CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WTKG-70  ;; CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/40
;; thetas out of sequence
  TVV2=THETA(2)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2)) 
  TVCL= THETA(1)   
  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1)) 
  K=CL/V2 
  ;; thetas out of sequence here
   K23=THETA(4)
 K32=THETA(5) 
    D1=THETA(6) *EXP(ETA(3)) ; infusion only ; include D1 and lag, with diag or block OMEGA
  
  TVKA=THETA(3) 
  KA=TVKA
  S2 	= V2/1000 
$ERROR     
 REP = IREP      
 IPRED =F  
 IOBS = F +EPS(1)
 Y=IOBS
$THETA  ;; must be one THETA per line.
 (0.001,100)	; THETA(1) CL UNITS =  L/HR
 (0.001,500) 	; THETA(2) V  UNITS = L
 (0.001,2) 	; THETA(3) KA UNITS = 1/HR 
;; test for comments in blocks
;; test for comments in blocks

   (0.001,0.02)  	 ;; THETA(4) K23 
 (0.001,0.3) 	 ;; THETA(5) K32 
 	 ;; init for K23~WT   ;; comment
;; test for comments in blocks
  
  
   (0.01,0.2) 		;; D1 THETA 
$OMEGA   ;; must be one ETA/line
  0.2  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE
$OMEGA
;; test for comments in blocks
  0.2 	; ETA(2) VOLUME
;; optional $OMEGA blocks
;; test for comments in blocks
 
$OMEGA ;; 3rd OMEGA block 
  0.1 		;; ETA(3) ETA ON ALAG1 		;; D1 ETA only 
$SIGMA  
;; test for comments in blocks

  3000 	; EPS(1) additive error
$EST METHOD=COND INTER MAX = 9999 MSFO=MSF1 
$COV UNCOND PRINT=E
 
 ;; Phenotype 
 ;; OrderedDict([('ADVAN', 1), ('K23~WT', 0), ('CL~WT', 0), ('CL~AGE', 0), ('ETAD1LAG', 1), ('D1LAG', 1), ('RESERR', 1)])
;; Genotype

$INPUT       ID TIME AMT DV WTKG GENDER AGE DROP

 (0.001,500) 	; THETA(2) V  UNITS = L
 (0.001,2) 	; THETA(3) KA UNITS = 1/HR
